from 'what?' to 'hah' in 30 seconds.

+ make sure 'hah.py' is on your $PYTHONPATH>
    $> export PYTHONPATH=/Users/fredrik/workspace/hah/lib
    $> # ymmv.

+ make sure irclib is installed>
    $> cd lib/python-irclib-0.4.8
    $> sudo python setup.py install

+ (optional:) make sure the tests pass>
	$> python tests/test_hah.py

+ go>
	$> python hah
